{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/ForwardSyntax.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Forward.matchApp?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Forward</span>.<span class=\"name\">matchApp?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> (<a href=\"./Init/Meta/Defs.html#Lean.Syntax.Term\">Term</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/ForwardSyntax.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ForwardArg\">ForwardArg</a>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `e` is a function application whose last argument effect-forwards into the enclosing `do`\nblock (its body bears a `do←` marker, possibly under `fun` binders), return the application\nhead sans the forwarding argument together with the `ForwardArg` description.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Do/ForwardSyntax.html#Lean.Elab.Do.Forward.matchApp?","kind":"def","line":26,"name":"Lean.Elab.Do.Forward.matchApp?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Do/ForwardSyntax.lean#L26-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/ForwardSyntax.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ForwardArg.body\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">ForwardArg</span>.<span class=\"name\">body</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Do/ForwardSyntax.html#Lean.Elab.Do.ForwardArg\">ForwardA